{
  "id": "virtuai-master",
  "name": "VirtuAI — Master Automation",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "name": "Manual run",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        200
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "Schedule 09:00",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        0,
        360
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 17 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "Schedule 17:00",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        0,
        520
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9090/n8n/trigger-pack",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 30000
        }
      },
      "name": "Start Pack (LIVE)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        300,
        360
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9090/run-crew",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 30000
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "{\n  \"build_only\": false,\n  \"llm\": \"kie\"\n}"
      },
      "name": "Run Crew (CrewAI 8 agents)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        300,
        700
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9090/agents/research/run-sync",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 120000
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "{\n  \"input\": { \"prompt\": \"Run your default task and return JSON.\" }\n}"
      },
      "name": "Run single Agent",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        300,
        860
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VirtuAI - Master Automation\n\n**Autopilot (auto-runs):**\nManual run / 09:00 / 17:00  ->  Start Pack (LIVE)\n= reel + portrait + carousel, published via /n8n/trigger-pack\n(the daily_pack path = the proven live results).\n\n**On-demand (click the node -> Execute step):**\n- Run Crew  -> /run-crew  (CrewAI 8-agent crew; set build_only:true for a free test)\n- Run single Agent -> /agents/{name}/run-sync\n\nBackend: FastAPI :9090 (must run with .env loaded).\nPoll progress: GET /status/{task_id}.\n\nNote: a webhook trigger was omitted - n8n 2.25.7 has a bug in its\nwebhook execution path in this build. Use Manual/Schedule or the\nFastAPI endpoints directly for external triggers.",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 470,
        "color": 4
      },
      "name": "Master automation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -520,
        200
      ]
    }
